            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 6168,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01K8Ne9JUTJER8Ar8ngJDv2T\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Let me try using the coder subagent to create the components:\"},{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_015qcZof1dkWenU7werqXQWg\",\"name\":\"task\",\"input\":{\"subagent_type\":\"coder\",\"description\":\"Create a Hero.tsx component at /src/components/Hero.tsx\\n\\nCOPY TO USE:\\n- Headline: \\\"Stop Scheduling Meetings. Start Having Them.\\\"\\n- Subheadline: \\\"Eliminate the endless back-and-forth across time zones. Our AI finds the perfect meeting time for your distributed team instantly—everyone just clicks yes.\\\"\\n- Primary CTA: \\\"Get Early Access\\\"\\n- Secondary CTA: \\\"See How It Works\\\"\\n- Trust indicator: \\\"Join 2,000+ distributed teams saving 80% on coordination time\\\"\\n\\nREQUIREMENTS:\\n- Use shadcn/ui components (Button, Input)\\n- Use theme color utilities only (bg-primary, text-primary, etc.)\\n- Include email signup form with Posthog tracking: posthog.capture('signup_completed', { section: 'hero' })\\n- Include secondary CTA button with Posthog tracking: posthog.capture('cta_clicked', { section: 'hero', type: 'secondary' })\\n- Add visual elements showing: Auto Time Zones, Smart Matching, Instant Results (use lucide-react icons: Globe, Calendar, Clock)\\n- Modern, clean design with gradient background\\n- Responsive layout\\n- Component should be under 150 lines\\n\\nReturn the complete file content.\"}},{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_018MjSPmmks2hBCgwhbgAVnH\",\"name\":\"task\",\"input\":{\"subagent_type\":\"coder\",\"description\":\"Create a Features.tsx component at /src/components/Features.tsx\\n\\nCOPY TO USE (4 features):\\n1. Title: \\\"Smart Time Zone Translation\\\"\\n   Description: \\\"Never calculate time zones again. Our AI automatically converts and displays meeting times in everyone's local timezone, eliminating confusion and missed meetings.\\\"\\n\\n2. Title: \\\"One-Click Calendar Sync\\\"\\n   Description: \\\"Connect Google, Outlook, or Apple Calendar in seconds. We instantly read your availability and keep everything synchronized across all your calendars.\\\"\\n\\n3. Title: \\\"Intelligent Availability Matching\\\"\\n   Description: \\\"Set your preferences once—working hours, buffer times, meeting limits. Our algorithm finds the perfect slots that respect everyone's schedule and work-life balance.\\\"\\n\\n4. Title: \\\"Instant Meeting Confirmation\\\"\\n   Description: \\\"Stop the email ping-pong. Share one link and get confirmed meeting times in minutes, not days. Everyone sees options that actually work.\\\"\\n\\nREQUIREMENTS:\\n- Use shadcn/ui components (Card)\\n- Use theme color utilities only (bg-primary, text-secondary, etc.)\\n- Add appropriate lucide-react icons for each feature (Globe, Calendar, Brain, Zap)\\n- Section headline: \\\"Everything You Need to Schedule Smarter\\\"\\n- Grid layout, responsive (2 columns on desktop, 1 on mobile)\\n- Clean, modern design\\n- Component should be under 150 lines\\n- Add id=\\\"features\\\" to the section for scroll navigation\\n\\nReturn the complete file content.\"}},{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01PqGRfR6K4smjuyqaPA1kn1\",\"name\":\"task\",\"input\":{\"subagent_type\":\"coder\",\"description\":\"Create a SocialProof.tsx component at /src/components/SocialProof.tsx\\n\\nCOPY TO USE:\\n- Headline: \\\"Trusted by Teams Who Value Their Time\\\"\\n- Stats:\\n  * \\\"2,000+\\\" - \\\"distributed teams scheduling smarter\\\"\\n  * \\\"80%\\\" - \\\"less time wasted on coordination\\\"\\n  * \\\"15 hours\\\" - \\\"saved per week per team\\\"\\n- Testimonial:\\n  * Quote: \\\"We used to spend entire mornings just finding times that worked across our US and Europe teams. Now it's instant. This tool gave us back our productivity.\\\"\\n  * Name: \\\"Sarah Chen\\\"\\n  * Title: \\\"VP of Operations, TechCorp\\\"\\n\\nREQUIREMENTS:\\n- Use shadcn/ui components (Card)\\n- Use theme color utilities only\\n- Display stats in a prominent grid (3 columns on desktop)\\n- Include testimonial card with quote styling\\n- Add star rating visual (5 stars) to testimonial\\n- Modern, credible design\\n- Responsive layout\\n- Component should be under 150 lines\\n\\nReturn the complete file content.\"}},{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_0127PfXNp879TWqUQkbiwKPD\",\"name\":\"task\",\"input\":{\"subagent_type\":\"coder\",\"description\":\"Create a CallToAction.tsx component at /src/components/CallToAction.tsx\\n\\nCOPY TO USE:\\n- Headline: \\\"Stop the Timezone Chaos. Start Scheduling Smarter.\\\"\\n- Subheadline: \\\"Join 500+ distributed teams who've eliminated scheduling headaches. Be first to access our launch pricing—lock in 40% off forever.\\\"\\n- Button text: \\\"Get Early Access\\\"\\n- Supporting text: \\\"No credit card required. Cancel anytime during free trial.\\\"\\n\\nREQUIREMENTS:\\n- Use shadcn/ui components (Button, Input)\\n- Use theme color utilities only\\n- Include email signup form with Posthog tracking: posthog.capture('signup_completed', { section: 'cta' })\\n- Prominent, centered design with gradient or colored background\\n- Add urgency/scarcity visual elements\\n- Responsive layout\\n- Component should be under 150 lines\\n\\nReturn the complete file content.\"}},{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_018YFZeZYSunyabw5EH5iex6\",\"name\":\"task\",\"input\":{\"subagent_type\":\"coder\",\"description\":\"Create a Footer.tsx component at /src/components/Footer.tsx\\n\\nREQUIREMENTS:\\n- Use shadcn/ui components as needed\\n- Use theme color utilities only\\n- Include:\\n  * Company name/logo text: \\\"ScheduleSmart\\\" (or similar scheduling tool name)\\n  * Tagline: \\\"Meeting coordination made effortless\\\"\\n  * Links sections: Product (Features, Pricing, Demo), Company (About, Blog, Careers), Legal (Privacy, Terms, Security)\\n  * Social media icon placeholders (Twitter, LinkedIn, GitHub) using lucide-react\\n  * Copyright text: \\\"© 2024 ScheduleSmart. All rights reserved.\\\"\\n- Clean, organized layout\\n- Responsive (stacked on mobile, columns on desktop)\\n- Component should be under 150 lines\\n\\nReturn the complete file content.\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":6,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":1596,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":11940,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":1596,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":1583,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
